2007-05-08  Takeshi Abe  <tabe@fixedpoint.jp>

	* release 0.1.1.

	* mm_avcodec.h, mm_avcodec.c, mm_ffmpeg.c: introduced 
	mm_avcodec_open and mm_avcodec_close, which are reentrant 
	cousins of avcodec_open and avcodec_close respectively 
	(inspired by gstreamer-ffmpeg).

